title: [DEV] Updated Sample to the new ARCommand API
message:
[DEV] Updated Sample to the new ARCommand API

The Unix Sample JumpingSumoPiloting is using the old API
(without libARController) and is listening for event (battery)
from the drone. So it was using the
ARCOMMANDS_Decoder_SetCommonCommonStateBatteryStateChangedCallback.

Created a decoder object, passed this decoder to the setter of
the callback, and at the end deleted the decoder.
